profile_positions.description:
Technology company focused on Business Intelligence and Analytics

Role: Responsible for the construction, presentation, and strengthening of the brand and support of the commercial area

Results:
- Implementation of a new commercial approach, which resulted in 25% efficiency gain for scheduling meetings;
- Acquisition of 3 new strategic partners in the first year;
- Implementation of the concept Good people make the difference around you which oriented all actions and communication strategies;
- Creation of the charity event Show de Bola Christmas, which served children from underprivileged communities. The event continued to exist even after my departure;
- Increase of 75% in the participation of the team in the company's social actions;
- Reformulation of the brand's presentation, with participation of the press and targeted ads in alternative media, which resulted in invitations for directors to participate in events as speakers

Role: Responsible for planning and execution of communications, support of the commercial area, internal communication, budget control, and contact with the communication agency.

Results:
- Unification of internal communication through the creation and implementation of the intranet and internal monthly newspaper, which eventually was also delivered to external customers;
- Reduction of 40% in the cost of communication materials by bringing production in-house;
- Strategic reorganization of announcements, reducing cost by 30%
- Implementation of New Ideas, a project that brought real case studies from the company to universities, offering students the opportunity to learn by practice, and bringing the company access to talent and new ways to solve problems.
